            <section>
               <title value="Hospital course note"/>
               <code>
                  <coding>
                     <system value="http://loinc.org"/>
                     <code value="8648-8"/>
                     <display value="Hospital course note"/>
                  </coding>
               </code>
               <text>
                  <status value="generated"/>
                  <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Dear colleague, I am writing to inform you regarding our shared patient, a 48-year-old male admitted for pre-renal transplant evaluation. During his stay from 12th to 18th March 2024, we completed a comprehensive transplant workup including cardiac assessment, vascular imaging, serological screening, and renal function studies. Tissue typing and crossmatch testing were performed, and infectious disease screening was completed satisfactorily. Urological evaluation confirmed suitability for transplantation. After multidisciplinary review, the patient was deemed an appropriate transplant candidate and has been formally listed on the transplant waiting list. Dialysis preparatory care planning has been initiated as per protocol pending organ availability. Please continue monitoring his current conservative management and ensure timely follow-up. Should his condition deteriorate or any concerns arise, please do not hesitate to contact our nephrology team directly.</div>
               </text>
            </section>
            <section>
